name: THESINS//005 : TWO HOURS LATE.
description:
ACT//005. LAKE HOUSE SCENE. 

‘I will kill him!’ Shouted Carl furiously. Of course he’s angry. May coming late to Lia’s party. Not only that, May lied about where’s she was before. Carl knew she was with Tom, yet May said she was at work. ‘You said it was over!’ 
‘Please let me go’. May cried, there was nothing she could do to calm him down. ‘Never! I will kill him. You’ll see. And you will live the rest of your miserable life knowing that it was you who make him dead.’ Tom left, didn’t care about May who’s trembling with fear . ‘I will kill Tom.’
